PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of David G.A. McLean, of Vancouver, British Columbia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian National Railway Company to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective August 31, 1994, in the place of Jacob Brouwer, whose term has expired.
